Juliana Taiwo-Obalonye, Abuja President Muhammadu Buhari has approved the appointment of Hon. Justice M.B. Dongban-Mensem as the Acting President of the Court of Appeal (PCA) with effect from June 3, 2020, for a another period of three months. According to a statement by Senior Special Assistant to the President on Media and Publicity, Garba Shehu, the extension is in pursuant to Section 238(4) and (5) of the Constitution of the Federal Republic of Nigeria, 1999 (as amended). 